        From here, each morning she wakes within the Schengen zone, she will
        both gain a day (from her previous trip aging out) and immediately spend
        that day's worth of allowance. Her balance isn't growing because she
        spends the freed days as they arrive — which permits her to remain in
        Schengen for a further 90 days, albeit perpetually on her 90th allowed
        day.
      </p>

